item.title: Home
item.description: Welcome to Yi-Yuan’s Website! Home Home Home Home Home My name is Yi-Yuan Li, a Civil Engineering M.Sc student at University of Macau, specializing in Structural Engineering. I am working in Dynamics & Monitoring laboratory under the supervision of Prof. Ka-Veng Yuen. My study interests: Structural Dynamics; Model Updating; Vibration Control; Structural Health Monitoring; System Identification; Modal Analysis; Earthquake Engineering. I’m ready to learn more about them any time! My skills: Matlab; Fortran My Curriculum Vitae My Statement of Interest
